fields.name: CurrentVersionedKeyIdentifier
fields.description: The object identifier of the current versioned Key Vault Key in use.

fields.name: KeyUri
fields.description: The object identifier for a key vault key object. When applied, the encryption scope will use the key referenced by the identifier to enable customer-managed key support on this encryption scope.

fields.name: LastKeyRotationTimestamp
fields.description: Timestamp of last rotation of the Key Vault Key.
